<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.4.7">
<l>eṉpiḻaikōp patupōlap paṉivāṭai yīrkiṉṟa</l>
<l>veṉpiḻaiyē niṉaintaruḷi yaruḷāta tirumālārk</l>
<l>keṉpiḻaittā ṭiruvaṭiyiṉ ṟakaviṉukkeṉ ṟoruvāycol</l>
<l>leṉpiḻaikku miḷaṅkiḷiyē yāṉvaḷartta nīyalaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As if stringing bones for jewels the chilly north winds saw.</l>
<l>To Tirumāl who is ungracious, graciously thinking of my failings</l>
<l>speak with one voice: “how did she fail in propriety against the holy feet?”,</l>
<l>young parrots who fail me. Won’t you, whom I have raised?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
